IceBBS-TERM
***********

   IceTERM is a special communications program designed for use with
bulletin board systems running IceBBS software.  This manual describes
the features of IceTERM programs up to version v119.

   A printed version of this manual is available from the Author (see
@{"Direct Updates" Link "Direct Updates"}) and may also be available from your local Amiga Dealer,
IceBBS sysop, or Amiga Users Group.  This 150 page manual includes
about 35 figures as well as this text and is printed in a small book
format (5x8 inch pages) and coil bound for ease of reference.  The
printed version includes the IceOLR manual in the same binding, so the
whole volume weighs in at about 200 pages.


